parameters:
Takumi: "I saw it on TV. Are you really going to the Avaran district
alone?"
Yui: "What are you talking about? There's no way I would go there..."
Takumi: "It's definitely a trap. Don't go!"

Yui: "That's what I'm saying, I'm not going! Pony Celes will take care
of Zydag for us."
Takumi: "No need to hide it anymore, I know you're Pony Celes."

Takumi: "No matter how much you try to hide it, I can tell. That's
what love is all about, right?"
Takumi: "...I'm really grateful for that time you saved me."
Takumi: "That's why I can't let you go there alone."
Takumi: "I'm hopelessly in love with you. I can't bear to lose you."

Takumi: "For your sake, I'd even fight Zydag. I wouldn't regret giving
my life for it."

Takumi: "It might be wrong to say this now, given the situation,
but..."
Takumi: "Will you go out with me?"

Yui: "It makes me genuinely happy to see you worry about me and
express your feelings so clearly."
Yui: "But... I can't return your feelings, Takumi-kun."

Takumi: "I don't need an answer right away. We've been through a lot
together, and I just want to get closer to you, little by little."
Yui: "I'm sorry, I have to be clear."

Takumi: "I was going to keep quiet because I didn't want to make you
sad, but I'll tell you what kind of guy Amasawa really is."

Takumi: "While Amasawa has been putting on a good face for you, he's
been dating Karen behind your back."
Takumi showed her a photo of Karen and \n[6] kissing.

Takumi: "It's not just kissing, those two apparently have a physical
relationship already."

Takumi: "I've been troubled by all the lovey-dovey stories Karen's
been telling me."

Takumi: "You can't trust someone who's two-timing. Right? Those are
the words you told me."

Takumi: "Even now, he's pretending to go to the Urban District but
he's actually heading to the Saionji family mansion."

Takumi: "He must have decided you can't beat Zydaug and is trying to
escape on his own."

Takumi: "I would never do something like that. Come with me, Morisaki!
I'll protect you from that guy Galves!"
Takumi: "Now, let me hear your answer."

\c[17]epending on your choice, you may be forced into a route leading
to a cuckoldry bad ending.
